---
title: Salmon & Garlic Veg Couscous Bowl with Herby Mayo
description: Bright, fresh and packed with goodness - this couscous bowl is a flavour powerhouse! Flaky, perfectly cooked salmon sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous packed full of all your favourite veg, tied together with a dreamy drizzle of creamy herby mayo. It’s wholesome, satisfying and just the right amount of fancy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67e0e9867594446a7cdcba01-be4a711b-0a54ee0e.jpeg
